snippet.title: Victim Complex - Gameplay Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Trailer 1 for Victim Complex, the upcoming horror simulator game by 5ive Bullet Games!

Use iconic ghost equipment like EMF Meters, Spirit Boxes, Quartz Crystals, and more to uncover the mystery of what happened at the abandoned apartment building in Victim Complex. Chapter One coming Summer 2024.

Wishlist now on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2840800/Victim_Complex/
